%F A124805 G.f.: (1 - x^2 - 4*x^3) / ((1 - x)*(1 - 3*x - 2*x^2)).
%F A124805 a(n) = 1 + ((3-sqrt(17))/2)^n + ((3+sqrt(17))/2)^n for n>0.
%F A124805 a(n) = 4*a(n-1) - a(n-2) - 2*a(n-3) for n > 3. (End)
